    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1912-11-09T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1912-11-09T00:00:00-05:00" n="1460"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d1460">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 817.00/2159.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">American Consul at Bluefields</gloss>
                        to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 86.]</seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Consulate</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Bluefields, Nicaragua</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1912-11-09">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 9, 1912</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: I have the honor to confirm the following
                    telegram to the Department, which was sent on October 16th by wireless via
                    Colón: <quote rend="blockquote">
                        <p>I have to suggest that the <hi rend="italic">Tacoma</hi> be withdrawn, as
                            there is no danger of any trouble now, all being quiet here.</p>
                    </quote>
                </p>
                <p>Thinking that the ship may be needed elsewhere, and as it appeared to me that all
                    danger had passed, I sent the above telegram. The ship received instructions on
                    October 19th to proceed to Tampico, Mexico.</p>
                <p>I have [etc.],</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Arthur J. Clare.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
